verbose_text: However, dietary l-isoleucine supplementation also enhanced the serum IgA, IgG, IFNbeta, IFNgamma, IL-1beta, TNF-alpha, and IL-10 levels and further promoted serum concentrations of these immunoglobulins and cytokines in the weaned piglets infected by RV (P < 0.05, Table XREF_TABLE).
